public class PerceivedCompletionTime
extends SimpleEvalFunc<Double>

Given a bag of (STime, ETime) pairs, the perceived duration is calculated. I.e., D = max(ETime)-min{STime}. This routine is involved in AEM model to calculate the activity completion time and session length.
